title: Punta San Pedro Airstrip
text:
Punta San Pedro Airstrip or Bahía Concepción Airstrip is a dirt <a href="airstrip">airstrip</a> in <a href="Muleg%C3%A9%20%28municipality%29">Municipality of Mulegé</a>, <a href="Baja%20California%20Sur">Baja California Sur</a> state, <a href="Mexico">Mexico</a>.
It is located south of <a href="Muleg%C3%A9">Mulegé</a> on <a href="Mexican%20Federal%20Highway%201">Mexican Federal Highway 1</a>, in the Bahía Concepción area.
The airstrip is used solely for <a href="general%20aviation">general aviation</a> purposes.
